### Generated docs ###
# AsciiDoc source lives under docs/; the rendered HTML is built into
# site/docs/ by `npm run docs:build` and also by CI before each Pages
# deploy (see .github/workflows/deploy-site.yml). Don't commit the
# generated output — it would clutter PR diffs and can drift from source.
/site/docs/

